OPTIVISION TECHN said unconsolidated sales
in May rose 51.38% to NT$92,536,000 from NT$61,127,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales             92,536           61,127    
YOY%              51.38%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            369,215          361,294    
YOY%              2.19%  
